org.nerd4j.csv.parser

Class CSVParserMetadata

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nerd4j.csv.parser.CSVParserMetadata

  • public final class CSVParserMetadata
extends Object
    Contains the meta-data needed to properly build a new CSVParser. This configuration is intended to be used with the CSVParserFactory.

    Unicode characters outside ASCII space won't be considered special at all and cannot have special functions.

    Author:
    Nerd4j Team
